bug = Bug(**bug_return['bugs'][0])
bug.depends_on.remove(123456)
bug.depends_on.append(145123)
output = bug.diff()
assert isinstance(output, dict)
assert output == {'depends_on': {'add': [145123], 'remove': [123456]}}
deps = bug.depends_on
assert isinstance(deps, list)
assert [145123] == deps
